long_description: The Chums Eiger Paracord Carabiner Keychain unravels to a 6-ft. length of strong parachute cord for emergencies or other uses. A stainless steel carabiner gives you attachment options. Survival keychain is made of a single 6-ft. length of 12-strand, 550-lb. rated parachute cord. Chums Eiger Paracord Carabiner Keychain features a stainless-steel carabiner on one end, key ring on the other.
